{"type":"message","id":"37bd1042","parentId":"81e4339d","timestamp":"2026-03-15T01:48:42.852Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要在 ClawHub 网站上找到 multi-search-engine 技能，并安装到本地。我需要使用 find-skills 技能来搜索这个技能，然后安装它。\n\n首先，我应该读取 find-skills 的 SKILL.md 来了解如何使用它。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我来帮你搜索并安装 multi-search-engine 技能。首先让我读取技能搜索工具的使用说明。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"read:0","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/skills/find-skills/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773539317214}}
{"type":"message","id":"a1ba7dc0","parentId":"37bd1042","timestamp":"2026-03-15T01:48:42.862Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"read:0","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: find-skills\ndescription: ClawHub技能搜索和发现工具，支持搜索、筛选、发现适合的技能。支持按功能、分类、评分、下载量筛选，提供技能详情、使用说明、安装指引。当用户需要找某个功能的技能、探索新技能时使用。\n---\n\n# Find Skills 技能搜索工具\n\n## 核心功能\n- 🔍 **技能搜索**：按关键词搜索ClawHub上的所有公开技能\n- 📊 **筛选功能**：按分类、评分、下载量、更新时间筛选技能\n- 📝 **技能详情**：查看技能的完整描述、功能说明、使用方法\n- ⭐ **评分系统**：查看其他用户对技能的评分和评价\n- 📈 **热门推荐**：推荐热门、高评分、新上线的技能\n- 📦 **一键安装**：直接安装选中的技能，自动解决依赖\n\n## 搜索语法\n- 普通关键词搜索：`find-skills \"web search\"`\n- 按分类搜索：`find-skills category:productivity`\n- 按评分筛选：`find-skills \"AI\" rating:>4.5`\n- 按下载量筛选：`find-skills \"git\" downloads:>1000`\n- 组合搜索：`find-skills \"frontend\" category:development rating:>4.0`\n\n## 使用示例\n```python\n# 搜索技能\nresults = search_skills(\"tavily search\", category=\"tools\", rating_min=4.0)\nfor skill in results:\n    print(f\"{skill['name']} - {skill['description']}\")\n    print(f\"评分: {skill['rating']} ⭐ 下载量: {skill['downloads']}\")\n\n# 安装技能\ninstall_skill(\"tavily-search\")\n```\n\n## 触发场景\n- 用户需要查找具有特定功能的技能\n- 想要探索新的技能，扩展功能\n- 寻找热门、高评分的优质技能\n- 需要了解某个技能的详细信息和使用方法\n- 比较多个同类技能的优缺点，选择最合适的\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773539322860}}
{"type":"message","id":"d30b16e8","parentId":"a1ba7dc0","timestamp":"2026-03-15T01:48:45.861Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到 find-skills 技能只提供了概念说明，但没有实际的工具调用命令。让我尝试通过 web_search 搜索 ClawHub 上的 multi-search-engine 技能。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我来搜索并安装 multi-search-engine 技能。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"web_search:1","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"site:clawhub.com multi-search-engine skill","count":5}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773539322863}}
