{"type":"message","id":"bac51acb","parentId":"4ecc1ad1","timestamp":"2026-03-15T02:23:06.377Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"从系统日志可以看到：\n1. `Exec completed (keen-bis, code 0) :: - Resolving multi-search-engine [32m√[39m OK. Installed multi-search-engine -> C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills\\multi-search-engine`\n\n这说明 **multi-search-engine 实际上已经成功安装了**！\n\n但是用户现在要求安装 **Web Search by Exa**，而从上面的结果看，这个技能已经安装了，提示 `Already installed`。\n\n我需要：\n1. 确认 multi-search-engine 确实已安装\n2. 确认 web-search-exa 确实已安装\n3. 向用户汇报两个技能的安装状态","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好消息！根据系统日志，实际上 **两个技能都已经成功安装**了！\n\n## ✅ 安装状态确认\n\n| 技能 | 状态 | 安装路径 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| **multi-search-engine** | ✅ 已安装 | `C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills\\multi-search-engine` |\n| **web-search-exa** | ✅ 已安装 | `C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills\\web-search-exa` |\n\n---\n\n## 📋 技能功能对比\n\n### 1️⃣ Multi Search Engine\n- **17个搜索引擎**（8个国内 + 9个国际）\n- 支持百度、Google、DuckDuckGo、WolframAlpha 等\n- **无需 API Key**\n- 适合多样化搜索需求\n\n### 2️⃣ Web Search by Exa\n- **神经网络搜索** - 语义理解而非关键词匹配\n- 支持代码搜索、公司研究、人员搜索\n- 支持深度研究和内容提取\n- **免费版有 generous 限制**，无需 API Key 即可使用基础功能\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 已就绪\n\n两个技能都已安装完成，可以立即使用！您可以根据需求选择：\n- 需要**多样化搜索引擎** → 使用 **Multi Search Engine**\n- 需要**AI 语义搜索/深度研究** → 使用 **Web Search by Exa**\n\n需要我演示如何使用其中任何一个技能吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773541365465}}
