{"type":"message","id":"6d09e3b4","parentId":"6a7810e8","timestamp":"2026-03-15T02:43:31.929Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"遇到了 API 速率限制，让我创建一个脚本来分批安装这些技能。由于之前的命令显示 `multi-search-engine` 和 `web-search-exa` 已经安装成功，我现在需要安装用户要求列表中的其他技能。但是 API 速率限制阻止了我直接安装，我需要向用户说明情况并提供解决方案。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我遇到了 **ClawHub API 速率限制**问题。这是为了防止过度调用而设置的保护机制。\n\n让我尝试另一种方式——通过浏览器直接从 GitHub 克隆仓库来安装这些技能："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"browser:123","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"open","url":"https://clawhub.com"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write:124","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace\\install_skills.ps1","content":"# 批量安装技能脚本\n$Skills = @(\n    \"skill-creator\",\n    \"model-usage\", \n    \"free-ride\",\n    \"copywriting\",\n    \"social-content\",\n    \"product-marketing-context\",\n    \"ui-ux-pro-max\",\n    \"diagram-generator\",\n    \"humanizer\",\n    \"openai-whisper\",\n    \"youtube-watcher\",\n    \"slack\",\n    \"api-gateway\",\n    \"mcporter\",\n    \"n8n\",\n    \"playwright-scraper\",\n    \"weather\"\n)\n\n$Workspace = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\\workspace\"\n$SkillsDir = \"$Workspace\\skills\"\n\n# 确保目录存在\nNew-Item -ItemType Directory -Force -Path $SkillsDir | Out-Null\n\n# 安装每个技能\nforeach ($Skill in $Skills) {\n    Write-Host \"Installing $Skill...\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n    try {\n        clawhub install $Skill\n        Write-Host \"✅ $Skill installed successfully\" -ForegroundColor Green\n    } catch {\n        Write-Host \"❌ Failed to install $Skill : $_\" -ForegroundColor Red\n    }\n}\n\nWrite-Host \"Installation complete!\" -ForegroundColor Cyan"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773542585552}}
