{"type":"message","id":"258f3f06","parentId":"3cf614bd","timestamp":"2026-03-15T03:45:47.844Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"目前遇到了严重的 **ClawHub API 速率限制** 问题。让我总结一下当前的情况，并提供实际的解决方案。\n\n## 📊 当前状态总结\n\n### ✅ 已成功安装的技能\n| 技能 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| `multi-search-engine` | ✅ 已安装 |\n| `web-search-exa` | ✅ 已安装 |\n\n### ❌ 安装失败的技能（速率限制）\n| 技能 | 失败原因 |\n|------|---------|\n| `skill-creator` | API Rate limit exceeded |\n| `model-usage` | API Rate limit exceeded |\n| `free-ride` | API Rate limit exceeded |\n| `copywriting` | API Rate limit exceeded |\n| `social-content` | API Rate limit exceeded |\n| ... 其他 12 个 | API Rate limit exceeded |\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 解决方案\n\n### 方案 1：等待后重试（推荐）\n\n\nAPI 限制每分钟 120 次请求，目前已经超出。建议等待 2-3 分钟后，分批安装剩余的技能。我可以创建一个脚本，在每个技能安装之间添加延时，避免再次触发限制。这样可以确保安装过程顺利完成，同时不会超出 API 的限制。\n\n接下来，我需要确认具体要安装的技能列表，然后制定一个合理的安装计划。\n\n关键技能包括 Skill Creator、Model Usage、Free Ride 和 Copywriting 等核心工具。这些技能涵盖了从创作到数据分析的多个领域。\n\n我将设计一个稳定的安装策略，通过设置合理的等待时间来避免系统限制，确保每个技能都能顺利安装。具体来说，我会在每个技能安装之间增加 5 秒的缓冲期，同时监控系统的响应状态。如果遇到限制，我会自动延长等待时间至 30 秒，确保安装流程不会因为系统限制而中断。现在遇到了 **ClawHub API 速率限制** 问题，这是为了防止过度调用而设置的保护机制（120 次/分钟）。\n\n让我为你提供一个**智能分批安装脚本**，可以自动处理速率限制：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write:138","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace\\install_skills_smart.bat","content":"@echo off\nchcp 65001 >nul\necho ========================================\necho Smart Skill Installation\necho ClawHub API Rate Limit Handler\necho ========================================\necho.\n\nset SKILLS=skill-creator model-usage free-ride copywriting social-content product-marketing-context ui-ux-pro-max diagram-generator humanizer openai-whisper youtube-watcher slack api-gateway mcporter n8n playwright-scraper weather\n\nset DELAY=3\nset RETRY_DELAY=30\nset COUNT=0\n\nfor %%S in (%SKILLS%) do (\n    set /a COUNT+=1\n    echo.\n    echo [%COUNT%/17] Installing: %%S\n    echo ----------------------------------------\n    \n    clawhub install %%S\n    \n    if %ERRORLEVEL% equ 0 (\n        echo [OK] %%S installed successfully\n    ) else (\n        echo [RATE LIMIT] Waiting %RETRY_DELAY% seconds...\n        timeout /t %RETRY_DELAY% /nobreak >nul\n        \n        clawhub install %%S\n        if %ERRORLEVEL% equ 0 (\n            echo [OK] %%S installed on retry\n        ) else (\n            echo [FAIL] %%S installation failed\n        )\n    )\n    \n    echo Waiting %DELAY% seconds before next...\n    timeout /t %DELAY% /nobreak >nul\n)\n\necho.\necho ========================================\necho Installation Complete!\necho ========================================\npause"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"read:139","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace\\install_skills_smart.bat"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write:140","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace\\INSTALL_README.md","content":"# Skill Installation Guide\n\n## Current Status\n\n### ✅ Already Installed (2/19)\n1. `multi-search-engine` - Multi-engine web search\n2. `web-search-exa` - Neural web search by Exa\n\n### ⏳ Pending Installation (17 skills)\n- skill-creator\n- model-usage\n- free-ride\n- copywriting\n- social-content\n- product-marketing-context\n- ui-ux-pro-max\n- diagram-generator\n- humanizer\n- openai-whisper\n- youtube-watcher\n- slack\n- api-gateway\n- mcporter\n- n8n\n- playwright-scraper\n- weather\n\n## Installation Options\n\n### Option 1: Automatic Retry (Recommended)\nRun the smart installer that handles rate limits automatically:\n```batch\ninstall_skills_smart.bat\n```\n\n### Option 2: Manual Installation\nWait 2-3 minutes for rate limit to reset, then:\n```bash\n# Install one by one with delays\nclawhub install skill-creator\n# wait 5 seconds\nclawhub install model-usage\n# ... continue\n```\n\n### Option 3: Off-Peak Installation\nInstall during off-peak hours when API usage is lower:\n- Late night (11 PM - 6 AM)\n- Early morning weekdays\n\n## Rate Limit Information\n\n- **Limit**: 120 requests per minute\n- **Current Issue**: Rate limit exceeded\n- **Reset Time**: Usually 1-2 minutes\n- **Strategy**: Batch with delays\n\n## Troubleshooting\n\n### If installation keeps failing:\n1. Check internet connection\n2. Verify GitHub access: `ping github.com`\n3. Try using VPN if in restricted region\n4. Check Windows Defender/Firewall settings\n\n### If rate limit persists:\n1. Wait 5 minutes and retry\n2. Install in smaller batches (3-5 at a time)\n3. Use `--force` flag if needed: `clawhub install skill-name --force`\n\n## Contact & Support\n\n- ClawHub Issues: https://github.com/openclaw/clawhub/issues\n- OpenClaw Discord: https://discord.com/invite/clawd\n- Documentation: https://docs.openclaw.ai\n\n---\nGenerated: $(Get-Date -Format \"yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss\")"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773546186033}}
